(6, 6, 'collection', 'Digital gadgets have become such an obsession. Exclusive for computer screens, blue block glasses release you from the irritation brought by the blue light glare from display screens.\r\n\r\nThe lenses come in plain glasses and are good for both cosmetic and prescription wearers. ', 0, 13),
(7, 7, 'collection', 'Don’t think black frames are dull and boring. The classic black can offer you an infinite variety: round frames, angular frames, thick arms and flat-top – you name it!\r\n\r\nThe subtle differences in the fine details make the ordinary truly extraordinary.', 0, 6),
(8, 8, 'nav_menu', '', 0, 1),
(9, 9, 'collection', 'Wanna put on a sophisticated elegant look at work or at school while staying away from the same old stuff?\r\n\r\nMetal frames must be your choice! Compared with the traditional metal frames, the eGG Metallia series attends particularly to shapes and colours, which are easy to carry, to accentuate the wearer’s youthfulness. ', 0, 10),
(10, 10, 'collection', 'An ultimate challenge of weight – from 12g to 11.5g, and here comes the Airy series with a mere 10g for the frame, all for your private ‘weightless’ experience!', 0, 15),
(11, 11, 'collection', 'Sunglasses are no longer confined to accessorising the summer look now. As a chic person, you’ll need a pair of edgy shades to go with your outfits for all seasons. The Solar glasses are a must-have on your list.', 0, 20),
(12, 12, 'collection', 'Small round metal circles, thin gold preppy-style frames, half-rims – the vintage trends have made a comeback.\r\n\r\nFine craftsmanship from eGG renders these frames a perfect blend of the retro style.', 0, 8),
(16, 16, 'nav_menu', '', 0, 7),
(17, 17, 'nav_menu', '', 0, 7),
(18, 18, 'nav_menu', '', 0, 1),
(19, 19, 'nav_menu', '', 0, 2),
(22, 22, 'collection', '數碼產品普及令人每日機不離手，要有效阻截由數碼產品屏幕發出嘅刺眼藍光，舒緩因藍光引起嘅眼部不適， blue block電腦屏幕專用眼鏡定可以幫到你。\r\n\r\n配備平光度數鏡片，特別照顧無近/遠/散光及配戴隱形眼鏡的上班一族。', 0, 13),
(23, 23, 'collection', '唔好以為黑框就毫無趣味, 經典黑框都可以好多變化! 圓框/ 方框 / 粗臂 / Flat-top, 每副Detail位都可以好唔一樣, 平凡中見不平凡。', 0, 6),
(24, 24, 'collection', '想「飛甩老套」, 但返工返學嘅你又要扮吓斯文, 唔洗左諗右諗, 金屬款最啱你!\r\n\r\n比較起舊式Metal, eGG從框形、用色著手, 令金屬架顏色簡單易Carry之餘, 設計上仲增添一份年輕感。 ', 0, 10),
(25, 25, 'collection', '挑戰更輕，由12g到11.5g，來到最近超輕系列，鏡架最輕只有10g！務求要帶比你超輕無重體驗', 0, 15),
(26, 26, 'collection', '今時今日, 太陽眼鏡已經唔再局限係夏日配飾。要躋身為潮人行列, 無論春夏秋冬, 都要有副型格黑超襯襯衫, 將太陽眼鏡變成你四季嘅Must-have item。', 0, 20),
(27, 27, 'collection', '「圓線細圈、金絲幼框、吊絲眉架」, 復古眼鏡元素一一浮現眼前。 eGG更利用精細手工, 務求塑造更完美產品, 糅合出完美復古風格。', 0, 8),
